gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Says Nath, "Came well, saint, see one's solitude; 
After that, many saints came out, some came out in temple complex, some became mediocre."

Here is the translation:

"Make a worthy mind take, Saints make silent become; 
After that, kings and rulers will speak, thus silence should not be for great ones."

Here is the translation:

Perform my longing, Lord, you are capable; 
I have conquered Girnar, make a beautiful temple there.
